('eightfold', 'Eightfold AI', 'Deep learning talent intelligence for skills-based hiring and retention',
 'Eightfold AI is a talent intelligence platform built on a deep learning model trained on hundreds of millions of career trajectories. The core insight is skills inference: Eightfold can determine what skills a person likely has based on their career path, even if those skills are not listed on their resume, and match them to roles requiring those skills. For hiring, this means surfacing candidates who would succeed in a role but might not apply because the job description does not match their self-description. For retention, it identifies employees at risk of leaving based on career trajectory patterns and surfaces internal opportunities before they look elsewhere. The platform integrates with most major ATS systems as an intelligence layer on top of existing workflows. Eightfold is particularly effective for companies that want to implement skills-based hiring - removing degree requirements and focusing on demonstrated capability - and need AI to make that operationally viable at scale. Used by major enterprises across financial services, healthcare, and technology.',
 'https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=eightfold.ai&sz=64',
